flowchart TB
    %% Actors
    Dev[Developer\n(Local Machine)]
    User[End User\nWeb Browser]

    %% GitHub
    Repo[GitHub Repository]
    Actions[GitHub Actions\n(CI/CD Runner)]

    %% Build
    Py[Python App / SSG\n(MkDocs / Pelican / Flask)]
    Artifacts[Static Files\nHTML / CSS / JS]

    %% Hosting
    Pages[GitHub Pages\n(CDN + HTTPS)]

    %% Development & Source Control
    Dev -->|Git over HTTPS\n(HTTP/1.1 or HTTP/2)| Repo

    %% CI/CD Trigger
    Repo -->|Webhook Event\nHTTPS + JSON| Actions

    %% Build Pipeline
    Actions -->|pip install\nHTTPS (PyPI)| Py
    Py -->|File I/O| Artifacts

    %% Deployment
    Actions -->|Git over HTTPS| Pages

    %% Runtime Access
    User -->|DNS (UDP/TCP 53)| Pages
    User -->|HTTPS\nHTTP/2 or HTTP/3| Pages
